      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Receipt, 27 July 1847, for $183.86 1/2 from Henry N. Bailey
         to Thomas Bailey being Henry Bailey's portion of the proceeds
         of the sale of the slaves from the estate of William
         Stanfield. This was pursuant to an order from the Halifax
         County, Virginia, court.</p>
